{"tid":499562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民僅餘不足3小時發言拉布","createTime":"2017-12-15T03:16:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T05:40:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d5a373345492f21d9d18786c053d42bba0a17fd9","tid":499562,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:16:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171215/20245215\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171215%2F20245215&d=b%2B13yFKnwMUrPr%2BsLJSIFTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=c24d170c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171215%2F20245215&h=ada6de9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171215/20245215</a><br />\n<br />\n泛民僅餘不足3小時發言拉布<br />\n<br />\n頭條   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】立法會昨日開始進入修改《議事規則》的辯論，由於主席梁君彥和代主席李慧琼為求盡快表決，懶理議會混亂，令民主派昨難以拉布，而11個民主派議員和熱血公民鄭松泰已經用盡15分鐘發言時間，當餘下11名民主派議員、合共約2小時45分鐘發言也用盡，《議事規則》修訂就會進行表決。<br />\n<br />\n由於提出決議案的公民黨楊岳橋和謝偉俊早前已完成首次發言，昨日大會先由另外10名提出決議案的議員作首次發言，之後再由同時提出決議案和修訂議案的議員逐一發言，最後每名議員可發言15分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171215/large/1214ralph4010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171215%2Flarge%2F1214ralph4010.jpg&h=0ce143dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有提出決議案的公民黨楊岳橋已完成首次發言。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n倘建制無人發言將表決<br />\n<br />\n據統計，民主派議員昨有26人次發言，其中胡志偉、張超雄、譚文豪等人因為提出決議案和修訂議案可有多於一次的發言機會，最終民主派約花6小時30分鐘發言時間，今日會議料會由民主派未作首次發言的民主黨鄺俊宇先發言，之後10名有提決議案和修訂案的民主派議員，將再有一次發言機會，若無建制派議員要求發言，就會進行表決。<br />\n<br />\n不過，由於民主派議員就廖長江的決議案提出23項修訂，預料有人會提出縮表決鐘的動議，民主派或可藉此再拉布，估計可拖延幾個小時，若民主派再無新招料今日內可表決。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t300人睇直播集氣<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t團體抗議立會「人大化」<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t【蘋果照相機】議會睡寶寶<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t反修改議規拉鋸戰　泛民響防狼器突襲為港發最後警號<br />\n頭條 5小時前"},{"pid":"f702fccdacc3b7cfa4c11da2ed71e20ad203bfab","tid":499562,"uid":31637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:20:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">300人睇直播集氣</span><br />\n粒元氣彈得鼻屎咁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110468f27ca55b0bfaa7e15d9ffd61a93aae7c3e","tid":499562,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:23:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">300人睇直播集氣</span><br />\n粒元氣彈得鼻屎咁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 達哥開台都多人過佢喇"},{"pid":"87ff146318fd4efd0f188f75e3a892311c7640ee","tid":499562,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1129b586473d7809e3072d657049a593e274d19","tid":499562,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:26:37.000Z","msg":"是但啦 快手過左佢唔好揼波鐘啦"},{"pid":"835995896174da90582956fbc7662ff382a66042","tid":499562,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:29:18.000Z","msg":"以前唔係杯葛拉布嘅咩？"},{"pid":"019d580a0af028e99cb1d4e1256416a641aabc13","tid":499562,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:47:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">300人睇直播集氣</span><br />\n粒元氣彈得鼻屎咁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 達哥開台都多人過佢喇</blockquote><br />\n達哥依加開會有幾多人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6623a47499f0dadbc389df355c03d06c2775fd3","tid":499562,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"